Zuckerman May Buy Goldman London Offices for $463 Million, Times Reports

-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 
2011-06-26T08:38:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-26/zuckerman-in-talks-to-buy-goldman-s-london-offices-times-says.html
Mortimer Zuckerman’s  Boston
Properties Inc. (BXP)  is in talks about buying  Goldman Sachs Group
Inc. (GS) ’s London offices in a 290 million-pound ($463 million)
transaction, the  Sunday Times reported .  Boston Properties is seeking to buy the offices at Daniel
House and Peterborough Court, the newspaper said, without saying
where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Martin in London at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Armstrong at   parmstrong10@bloomberg.net  